          boolean pyro_damage

        • slow_damage

          boolean slow_damage
          Determines whether the tower delivers slow damage on an attack.

        • attack_mode

          Tower.AI_TYPE attack_mode
          Indicates which type of attack pattern the tower should follow when attacking. FOLLOW: Attacks the critter closest to the entrance in range and continues attacking this critter until it is out of range. BACK_FIRST: Attacks the critter closest to the entrance in range. FRONT_FIRST: Attacks the critter closest to the exit in range. RADIAL: Attacks radially (special AI for radial tower).

        • active

          boolean active
          True if the tower is allowed to fire.
